race.comment: DEADLY AVENGER (6) is first up since finishing fourth (30.69) in a NG at Wagga over 525m ten weeks ago. Form here at this distance is sound. Good overall strike-rate and expected to feature. PAW OSWALD (7) filled the minor placings again last time when second (29.27) at this track, making it three straight minors on end. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Expected to feature on best form. ETHANOL SECRET (3) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at this track but was a Special conditions H winner two back at this track. Rates a winning chance on best. OVERLAND BOY (1) was well supported last time but could only manage second (26.03), beaten 0.8 lengths. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Racing well and deserves a win.
